{"tid":339262,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"貌似Stephy無人追 　小麗老師六十歲先嫁？","createTime":"2017-07-29T02:08:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T05:36:50.000Z","uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":46,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8877fd59e9f81fc83777003b899c08507fd20810","tid":339262,"uid":55851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:08:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://vmagimg.next.hk/images/apple/20170727/large/1501143446_484f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fvmagimg.next.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple%2F20170727%2Flarge%2F1501143446_484f.jpg&h=3b0d70cd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20161003/photo/1003-00176-077b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161003%2Fphoto%2F1003-00176-077b1.jpg&h=7956ab55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.playbuzz.com/cdn/dd311a02-3830-4989-961b-43d075db8659/566503bf-b322-4adf-b3ef-cc9cc9a4fdb0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.playbuzz.com%2Fcdn%2Fdd311a02-3830-4989-961b-43d075db8659%2F566503bf-b322-4adf-b3ef-cc9cc9a4fdb0.jpg&h=a88fa07e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n雨傘運動期間劉小麗決志，用十年負起知識分子使命，為香港付出，莫非十年不嫁？她道：「我從來沒有用婚姻作為一種想法，如果婚姻要被犧牲，就被犧牲吧，這對我不是很大的問題。」她告訴記者，早年在中大當助教時學生指她貌似Stephy鄧麗欣，訪問這天看清楚果然相像幾分。<br />\n<br />\n《一代宗師》宮二奉道，一生信守誓言，不婚嫁，不留後，不傳藝；小麗傳藝（教副學士，目前請假），未必婚嫁留後，反正忙於拯救眾生，情愛小事靠邊站，「其實並無拍拖時間，放工回家其實我比較珍惜一個人放空發呆的時間，我是一個比較毒（獨）的人。」<br />\n<br />\n如今無伴，也沒有追求者，「連記者找我，我也不是每次回覆，怎樣追求？我不是上班開會，就是搞墟，見民間組織、記者，以及發呆放空，哪有一個可被追求的狀態？」總想有人抱抱吧？「也有想的時候，但沒有基礎也沒辦法啊。人生不會所有事都得到，我所憧憬的理想，我有幸有空間可以實踐，對我來說是最大幸福。」<br />\n<br />\n自言不介意六十歲才嫁。須知道香港男人多數以貌娶人，女人多數待嫁而姑──等着等着變了阿姑。「那便不結吧，其實我真的不介意。我也不是獨身主義，但如果要我捨割一樣東西，來換取空間承擔很多東西，我願意。」話說早年教務繁重，媽媽病重，自己又初次接觸社運，透不過氣，「當時我剛剛分手，正在刷牙，覺得幸好我分了手，少打一份工，可以做到很多事。」<br />\n<br />\n撰文：陳勝藍<br />\n攝錄：鄭樹清<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170728/534144\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170728%2F534144&d=OBmMLW3ZCeYTmCBe%2FFpp%2BzA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=d85287c0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnextplus.nextmedia.com%2Fnews%2Flatest%2F20170728%2F534144&h=e1ae8480\" target=\"_blank\">http://nextplus.nextmedia.com/news/latest/20170728/534144</a>"},{"pid":"fd098783a4a36be57c58d7c3189c0fa0bba1b3d6","tid":339262,"uid":105678,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:33:24.000Z","msg":"咁撚樣衰，又臭格，搵鬼要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2da088a06d4f821a9e60b08ed757551aba7ed5d2","tid":339262,"uid":102096,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6092a7d29fa9c75167b0324de14bac7e390ede25","tid":339262,"uid":125310,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:39:57.000Z","msg":"快撚啲驗眼"},{"pid":"8b234b33b3860270767ca4775623ed737515e045","tid":339262,"uid":130105,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:47:28.000Z","msg":"咁都話似 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6348211ed7ad3bd7d1f92229f83d98312224d478","tid":339262,"uid":50595,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:52:22.000Z","msg":"哪裡來的自信 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1711934d043db908ac355db4a7d3e6f9ad7b995a","tid":339262,"uid":615,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"邊忽似<br />\n唔好影衰我女神"},{"pid":"381afc122f5095b869de47ac6dc7d2e07fff2a6c","tid":339262,"uid":42820,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:06:51.000Z","msg":"咁嘅時勢仲訪問呢D"},{"pid":"18c53c46ea6f1df6f3c85c59f94324ac838080a8","tid":339262,"uid":55851,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-29T03:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁嘅時勢仲訪問呢D</blockquote><br />\n徵婚廣告嚟，撈唔掂咪吊金龜嫁咗佢就算<img src=\"/assets/faces/no